====== README ======

  * Name : MakeMyDay
  * Desc : Dokuwiki template for PGDay.fr 2008
  * Author : damien.clochard@dalibo.com
  * License : BSD
  * Date : september 2008 

===== DEMO =====

This template is used there : http://2008.pgday.fr

===== REQUIREMENT =====

This theme was used with the following plug-ins. They might not be mandatory, but they're very useful :

  * Formular : http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugin:form 
  * GoogleMaps : http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugin:googlemaps 

===== INSTALL =====
 
  - Just copy this directory in dokuwiki's lib/tpl/ folder
  - Go to the admin page and select this template

===== SPECIAL PAGES =====

There 2 special pages :

-> The Navigation bar is a standalone wiki page called "nav". 
So you can edit the nav bar very simply : just go to the url :

http://your.wiki.address/nav?do=edit

-> The sponsor sidebar can be edited too. The url is :

http://your.wiki.address/sponsors?do=edit

